      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just not just a feeling though. it's real. it feels like there's nothing left for me to be. everyone's only ever known that version of me, and now that it's gone, there's just this empty shell. why should i keep pretending to be someone i'm not anymore? it's exhausting.",
